<p>this is controller</p>  <pre><code>@ManagedBean @ViewScoped public class DeviceController implements Serializable {     private Device device;      private List&lt;Device&gt; deviceList;      @ManagedProperty("#deviceService")     private DeviceService deviceService;      public DeviceController() {         deviceList = new ArrayList&lt;Device&gt;();     }      @PostConstruct     public void init(){         setDeviceList(getDeviceService().getDeviceList());     } </code></pre>  <p>and this is service class, and i get the error "Unable to set property deviceService for managed bean deviceController" during running the project</p>  <pre><code>@ManagedBean(name = "deviceService") @ApplicationScoped  public class DeviceService {      @ManagedProperty("#{deviceDaoImpl}")     DeviceDaoImpl devicedaoimpl;      public void addDevice(Device device) {         devicedaoimpl.addDevice(device);     }      public List&lt;Device&gt; getDeviceList() {         return devicedaoimpl.getDeviceList();     } </code></pre>